text: Nasir Nawaz (born 5 October 1998) is a Pakistani cricketer. He made his List A debut for Punjab in the 2017 Pakistan Cup on 19 April 2017. Prior to his List A debut, he was named as captain of Pakistan's squad for the 2016 Under-19 Asia Cup. He made his Twenty20 debut for Rawalpindi in the 2017–18 National T20 Cup on 12 November 2017. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Pakistani cricketers Category:Punjab (Pakistan) cricketers Category:Rawalpindi cricketers Category:People from Rawalpindi Category:Islamabad United cricketers
